public Object chain(Object val, Function ... functions) {
    Object nextInput = functions[0].apply(val);
    if (functions.length == 1) return nextInput;
    Function[] tail = Arrays.copyOfRange(functions, 1, functions.length);
    return chain(nextInput, tail);
}
```

